@startuml
!theme plain
actor User as "Employee / Owner"
participant UI as "Activity / Fragment"
participant AppViewModel as "AppViewModel"
participant AppRepository as "CoffeeOrderRepository"
participant KtorServer as "Ktor Backend"

User -> UI: Tương tác (VD: Mở danh sách bàn)
UI -> AppViewModel: Gửi event (VD: fetchTables())
activate AppViewModel
AppViewModel -> AppViewModel: Cập nhật State (isLoading = true)
AppViewModel -> AppRepository: Gọi API (VD: getAllTable())
activate AppRepository

AppRepository -> KtorServer: Gửi Request HTTP/GET
activate KtorServer
KtorServer -> KtorServer: Truy vấn Database
KtorServer --> AppRepository: Trả về HTTP 200 (JSON DTOs)
deactivate KtorServer

AppRepository --> AppViewModel: Trả về Result.success(tables)
deactivate AppRepository

AppViewModel -> AppViewModel: Cập nhật State với dữ liệu mới
AppViewModel -> AppViewModel: Cập nhật State (isLoading = false)
AppViewModel --> UI: Render UI với State mới
deactivate AppViewModel
@enduml
